<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q33_v5" title="Q33_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Una empresa de buses modela la cantidad de pasajeros transportados en un día (en cientos) para tres recorridos, en función de la cantidad <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> (en cientos) de pasajeros de un recorrido base. Se tienen los siguientes modelos:</p>
    <div>
      <m:math>
        <m:mtable>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mtext>Recorrido 1</m:mtext></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mtext>Recorrido 2</m:mtext></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mtext>Recorrido 3</m:mtext></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
        </m:mtable>
      </m:math>
    </div>
    <p>Si en el recorrido 1 viajan menos pasajeros que en conjunto en los recorridos 2 y 3, ¿cuál de las siguientes inecuaciones representa la información entregada?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>&lt;</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>&lt;</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>&gt;</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>&gt;</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
